text: Dongying () is a prefecture-level city in northern Shandong province, China. In 2020, 2,193,518 people lived there. == Administration == Dongying administers three districts and two counties: * Dongying District () * Hekou District () * Kenli District () * Guangrao County () * Lijin County () Category:Cities in China Category:Shandong
title: Dongying
